headline: b'Tech CEOs Call for Gun Control Following YouTube Shooting'
snippet: b'Several Silicon Valley leaders called for increased gun control on Tuesday afternoon after a woman at the headquarters of YouTube shot and wounded three people before taking her own life.'

headline: b'Democrats in New York State Senate Reconcile After Years of Infighting'
